Subject: [PATCH 1/2] Add Pricing, Privacy Policy, and Terms of Service pages

Ports the three static mockup pages into the React app as routes
(/pricing, /privacy, /terms), rebuilt with the product's real dark/light
design system (Sora + IBM Plex Mono, brand-violet/cyan, existing Table and
Button components) instead of the mockups' standalone teal palette.
Content is preserved verbatim, including bracketed legal placeholders.
Wires up the dead Terms/Privacy footer links on the landing page.

