+            </td>
+            <td>IP address, browser type, request logs</td>
+            <td>Security, rate limiting, debugging</td>
+          </tr>
+        </tbody>
+      </table>
+      <p>
+        We do not intentionally collect special-category data. Do not connect APIs containing data you are
