+      </p>
+
+      <h2>3. How We Use Data</h2>
+      <ul>
+        <li>To provide, secure, and improve the Service (legal basis: contract performance and legitimate interests).</li>
+        <li>To process payments and manage subscriptions (contract performance).</li>
+        <li>
